Venn Diagram

Source: R/venn.h.R
venn.Rd

Venn Diagram

Usage

venn(data, var1, var1true, var2, var2true, var3, var3true, var4, var4true)

Arguments

data

The data as a data frame.

var1

a string naming the variable from data that contains the the first variable used for the report

var1true

a string naming the level from var1 that contains the the true level

var2

a string naming the variable from data that contains the the second variable used for the report

var2true

a string naming the level from var2 that contains the the true level

var3

a string naming the variable from data that contains the the third variable used for the report

var3true

a string naming the level from var3 that contains the the true level

var4

a string naming the variable from data that contains the the fourth variable used for the report

var4true

a string naming the level from var4 that contains the the true level

Value

A results object containing:

results$todoa html
results$plotan image
results$plot2an image
